---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Security & Penetration Testing Blog | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="Expert insights on penetration testing, cybersecurity best practices, and how to protect your Texas business. Learn about costs, frequency, red teaming, and more." showMatrix={true}>
  <section>
    <h1>Security Blog</h1>
    <p class="lead">Expert insights on penetration testing, cybersecurity best practices, and protecting your Texas business. Learn from our experienced team about security assessments, compliance, and building a stronger security program.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="posts">
    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/penetration-testing-costs-roi">Penetration Testing Costs & ROI: Why The Investment Pays Off</a></h2>
      <p>Understand penetration testing pricing, budget considerations, and the real ROI of security testing compared to the cost of a breach.</p>
      <a href="/blog/penetration-testing-costs-roi" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/red-teaming-vs-pentesting">Red Teaming vs Penetration Testing: Complete Comparison Guide</a></h2>
      <p>Comprehensive guide comparing red teaming and penetration testing. Learn which approach is right for your organization and understand the key differences.</p>
      <a href="/blog/red-teaming-vs-pentesting" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/how-often-should-you-pentest">How Often Should You Conduct Penetration Testing?</a></h2>
      <p>Complete guide to testing frequency based on industry, risk profile, and compliance requirements. Learn when annual testing is enough and when you need more.</p>
      <a href="/blog/how-often-should-you-pentest" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/5-signs-your-business-needs-pentest">5 Signs Your Business Needs a Penetration Test</a></h2>
      <p>Not sure if your business needs penetration testing? Here are 5 clear signs that indicate it's time to test your security posture.</p>
      <a href="/blog/5-signs-your-business-needs-pentest" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/why-choose-local-security-consultant">Why Choose a Local Security Consultant?</a></h2>
      <p>Working with a local penetration testing company in Bulverde, Spring Branch, or San Antonio offers real advantages. Learn why local matters for your business security.</p>
      <a href="/blog/why-choose-local-security-consultant" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/common-vulnerabilities-small-business">Common Vulnerabilities in Small Business Networks</a></h2>
      <p>Small businesses face real security threats. Learn about the most common vulnerabilities we find in Texas small business networks and how to address them.</p>
      <a href="/blog/common-vulnerabilities-small-business" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2><a href="/blog/what-is-penetration-testing">What is Penetration Testing?</a></h2>
      <p>Learn what penetration testing is and why your Texas business needs it. Discover how ethical hackers identify vulnerabilities before cybercriminals do.</p>
      <a href="/blog/what-is-penetration-testing" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Have a Security Question?</h2>
    <p>Can't find what you're looking for? Contact us to discuss your penetration testing needs.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead { 
    font-size: 1.25rem; 
    max-width: 700px; 
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  section { 
    margin-bottom: 3rem; 
  }
  
  .posts { 
    display: grid; 
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  article { 
    background: var(--bg-alt); 
    padding: 1.5rem; 
    border-radius: 8px; 
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  
  article:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  article h2 { 
    margin-top: 0; 
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  article h2 a { 
    color: var(--text); 
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  article h2 a:hover { 
    color: var(--accent); 
  }
  
  article p { 
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .read-more { 
    color: var(--accent); 
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .read-more:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .cta {
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
</style>
